<HEADLINE> Greece to Provide for Maintenance of French Jet Fighters </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, October 3 (Xinhua) -- The Hellenic Aerospace Industry
(EAB) today signed a major agreement providing for the maintenance
of French mirage f-1 jet fighters by EAB.
</P>
<P>
