Atlanta Games. It was a demonstration of what she had learned and
had been trained for after so long," she said.
</P>
<P>
Yu thinks Guo Jingjing, another teenager diver under her
instruction, failed to perform well enough for a medal at Atlanta
just due to huge ressure on herself.
</P>
<P>
"She can improve herself year by year and I hope she would be
really ready by the year for the 2000 Olympics in Sydney," Yu
said. 
