Arantxa Sanchez Vicario of Spain, coming off a disappointing
performance at last weekend's Fed Cup competition against the
United States, advanced to the quarterfinals Thursday with a 6-2,
6-1 win over Miriam Oremans of the Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
Fifth-seeded American Lindsay Davenport also won her
second-round match, 7-6 (7-0), 6-1, over Els Callens of Belgium.
</P>
<P>
Davenport, who won both her singles matches at the Fed Cup,
will meet third seed Iva Majoli of Croatia in the quarterfinals.
