<HEADLINE> Medical Center To Treat Tuberculosis In Lhasa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 4 (Xinhua) -- A medical center to control
tuberculous has been built in Lhasa, capital of Southwest China's
Tibet Autonomous Region, Health News reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
