Indian state and was missing since Wednesday night, had gone to
Bhangapara to collect some money he lent earlier.
</P>
<P>
Enraged over the killing, villagers of Rabanpur attacked
Bhangapara and torched about 156 houses in the village.
</P>
<P>
Twenty-three persons have been arrested for the incident.
